        "sendTo": "alexanderkoelnberger@gmail.com",
        "subject": "=☀️ {{ $('Merge All RSS Feeds').itemMatching(0).json.count || $input.all().length }} neue Cloud Security Jobs für dich!",
        "emailType": "html",
        "message": "=<html>\n<body style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;\">\n  <h2>Moin Alexander! 👋</h2>\n  <p>Ich habe <strong>{{ $input.all().length }}</strong> neue passende Jobs gefunden:</p>\n  \n  {{ $input.all().map((item, index) => `\n    <div style=\"border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; background: #f9f9f9;\">\n      <h3 style=\"color: #2563eb; margin-top: 0;\">📋 ${item.json.title}</h3>\n      <p><strong>🏢 Firma:</strong> ${item.json.creator || item.json.author || 'Unbekannt'}</p>\n      <p><strong>⭐ Score:</strong> ${item.json.score}/10</p>\n      <p><strong>🔗 Link:</strong> <a href=\"${item.json.link}\" style=\"color: #2563eb;\">${item.json.link}</a></p>\n      \n      <p><strong>💡 WARUM PASST ES:</strong></p>\n      <ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\">\n        ${item.json.contentSnippet.toLowerCase().includes('azure') ? '<li>✅ Azure/Cloud Security Match</li>' : ''}\n        ${item.json.contentSnippet.toLowerCase().includes('remote') || item.json.contentSnippet.toLowerCase().includes('hybrid') ? '<li>✅ Remote/Hybrid möglich</li>' : ''}\n        ${item.json.contentSnippet.toLowerCase().includes('devops') || item.json.contentSnippet.toLowerCase().includes('ci/cd') ? '<li>✅ DevOps/CI-CD Erfahrung gefragt</li>' : ''}\n        <li>✅ Passt zu deinen Skills: DevSecOps, Zero-Trust, AI</li>\n      </ul>\n      \n      <p><strong>📝 BESCHREIBUNG (Auszug):</strong></p>\n      <p style=\"font-size: 0.9em; color: #666;\">${item.json.contentSnippet.substring(0, 300)}...</p>\n    </div>\n  `).join('') }}\n  \n  <hr style=\"margin: 30px 0;\">\n  <p>👉 <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/DEINE_SHEET_ID\" style=\"color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;\">Öffne dein Google Sheet</a></p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em;\">Viel Erfolg! 🚀</p>\n</body>\n</html>",
        "options": {}
